sentences: Martin Blanes (born 1980 in Ourense, Spain) is a Galician guitarist, ethnomusicologist and composer.
In 2009, he performed in Argentina, Germany, Japan, Poland and USA.
In 2008 he released his CD O Son da Lenda (The Sound of the Legend) that consists of 12 tracks inspired by Galician legends and the music of that region.
During 2009 he released two CDs as leader.
He co-wrote, together with Lloren√ß Barber, the inaugural work for pilgrimage year of Saint Iacobus tomb event "Xacobeo 99".
